  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, the average electric bill for a 2-bedroom apartment in the Bay Area typically ranges from $100 to $200 per month. However, this can vary widely depending on factors such as energy usage, the specific location within the Bay Area, the time of year, and whether the apartment has electric heating or cooling systems.\n\nFor the most accurate and current figures, it\u2019s advisable to check with local utility providers or consult recent reports specific to the region.",
